{
  "text": "In this research the quantitative method will be applied since it follows the procedure of collecting numerical and statistical information and process it using computational techniques and specifying it to a group of people to identify a phenomena. This methods gives an advantage by selecting a bigger sample of candidates, thus provide an accurate result and a wider comprehensive overview. [CITATION_1] ",
